- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper considers fair allocation of land plots, which is a real-world problem that can be tackled using AI techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes algorithms for finding good allocations, which can be seen as a form of machine learning.
